name: Roll-Up Change Mat
description: Great to pop in your babys nappy bag. Perfect so they don't get germs that exist on shopping centre change tables. Rolls up to approx. 25cm diametre with fabric covered elastic loops. Simply unroll and use to protect your precious child from germs. Fully washable and dryer safe too! Measures 60cm x 40cm. Made from 100% cotton fabric with polyester wadding.
